data: Timer
Tsiânn-tsai ê tsí-ū decoder ê transformer
Iûnn-ha̍p ê sūn-sū keh-sik, iōng-tsāi bô-kâng luī-hîng ê tsu-liāu
Iōng 1-5% ê tsu-liāu, ū kiông-khióng ê few-shot piáu-hiān
MOMENT
Khai-hòng guân-bé ê ki-tshóo mô-hîn ka-tso̍k
To-tshu tsu-liāu ê hùn-liān tsiàn-lio̍k
Tī iú-hān kàm-tok hā, ū tshut-sik ê piáu-hiān
TimeMixer
To-tshú-tōo ê MLP kiat-kòo
Khó-tsiah-kái ê hūn-ha̍p tsoo-kiānn, iōng-tsāi sî-khiok bôo-sik
Tī 18 ê piau-tsún tē-tiám ta̍t-kàu SOTA
TimesNet
To-tsiu-kî hun-sik
Uì 1D tsuán 2D, iōng-tsāi sî-khiok bôo-sik
Tī 5 ê tsú-iàu jīm-bū ta̍t-kàu iûnn-ha̍p ê piáu-hiān
PatchTST
I-kù patch ê sî-khiok tsu-liāu tshú-lí
Bô-kâng thong-tōo ê transformer
Tī tn̂g-kî ī-tshik siōng, kiám-tsió 21% ê MSE
